headline: The Home Depot Announces Exclusive KILZ® Brand Agreement
summary: The Home Depot and Behr Paint Company have expanded their long-term relationship to exclusively offer KILZ® branded primer products in the United States and Puerto Rico. The Home Depot will become the only home improvement big box retailer to offer KILZ® branded primer products including KILZ Original®, KILZ PVA®, KILZ 2®, KILZ 3 Premium®, KILZ Restoration® and KILZ Mold & Mildew® and more problem-solving primer products and aerosols.

headline: Home Depot Director Bought Up $1 Million of Stock
summary: Home Depot  stock is in a post-earnings slump, and one director bought a large block of shares of the home-improvement retailer.  It was the first insider stock buy in years for the company.  Home Depot reported strong fourth-quarter earnings before the market opened Feb. 25, and even raised its dividend.
